[police siren]

00:26.680 --> 00:27.480
Jesus!

00:27.600 --> 00:28.920
Phinneus!

00:29.040 --> 00:30.280
I thought this was meantto be a doddle to you.

00:30.400 --> 00:31.200
It's fine.

00:33.920 --> 00:35.160
[inaudible]

00:35.280 --> 00:37.080
Don't you start.
We're all good here.

00:44.520 --> 00:45.320
Drive!

00:45.440 --> 00:46.200
Not yet.

00:52.480 --> 00:53.920
Can we go home now?

00:54.040 --> 00:55.280
We'll see.

00:55.400 --> 00:56.320
C'mon, Ted.

00:56.440 --> 00:57.560
The ladies will be missing us.

00:57.680 --> 01:01.400
These ladies
include your wife?

01:01.520 --> 01:04.720
[police siren]

01:05.800 --> 01:06.680
Now drive.

01:09.760 --> 01:12.720
Well, sometimes it's goodfor the ladies to miss us.

01:12.840 --> 01:13.800
Makes them appreciate us more.

01:21.880 --> 01:24.440
Did I mention that Ilike it when Ted goes away?

01:24.560 --> 01:26.160
Yes, Pat, you did.

01:26.280 --> 01:29.160
Get back to work.

01:29.280 --> 01:30.680
[THEME - HELLO SAILOR, "WATCH YOUR BACK"]

01:30.800 --> 01:32.640
[SINGING] Watch your
back when you're

01:32.760 --> 01:34.640
walking down the alleys, child.

01:34.760 --> 01:39.640
Watch your back when you're out.

01:39.760 --> 01:42.600
There's a stranger on
the street these days.

