ROD: [sighs]

15:03.480 --> 15:04.280
How much?

15:11.040 --> 15:11.880
Miss Ngaire.

15:12.000 --> 15:12.800
Hm.

15:16.120 --> 15:18.640
Oy, Rod.

15:18.760 --> 15:19.880
How much?

15:20.000 --> 15:21.960
Look, these are
tough times, Lefty.

15:22.080 --> 15:22.920
How much?

15:25.720 --> 15:28.800
[slurping]

15:28.920 --> 15:31.880
I now get the importanceof this tree to you fellas,

15:32.000 --> 15:33.840
and I hope that we
can work together

15:33.960 --> 15:37.040
to do what must be done.

15:37.160 --> 15:41.560
Like, maybe plant another one.

15:41.680 --> 15:44.120
To celebrate, you know, the--

15:44.240 --> 15:45.080
neighborhood.

15:48.040 --> 15:52.040
That would be honorable thing.

15:52.160 --> 15:53.640
Well, then, welcome
to our street.

15:56.560 --> 15:57.640
We should drink on this.

15:57.760 --> 15:59.920
A little.

16:00.040 --> 16:00.960
[kissing ]

16:01.080 --> 16:02.360
I'm Darijo.

16:02.480 --> 16:04.000
You like wine, Ted?

16:04.120 --> 16:06.760
Uh, I'm more of a beer man.

16:06.880 --> 16:07.800
Here we drink wine.

16:10.440 --> 16:13.440
Did you know that they'vebeen here for years,

16:13.560 --> 16:16.160
and they practically
built Marsden Point.

16:16.280 --> 16:17.480
And they're really good people.

16:17.600 --> 16:18.880
If you gave 'em a
chance, you'd love them.

16:22.800 --> 16:24.040
And it's all sorted.

16:24.160 --> 16:27.280
It's all good, so don't
worry your pretty head.

16:27.400 --> 16:28.440
LEFTY: Knock, knock.

16:28.560 --> 16:29.360
TED: Lefty!

16:29.480 --> 16:30.800
Come have some wine.

16:30.920 --> 16:31.800
OK.

16:31.920 --> 16:33.920
Someone's having a good night.

16:34.040 --> 16:36.520
All right, me and Ngaireare off to the Hungry Horse.

16:36.640 --> 16:38.280
But, uh, let me add to the joy.

16:38.400 --> 16:39.480
Your wages from the
leftover jewels.

16:43.120 --> 16:43.920
Is this it?

16:44.040 --> 16:45.480
Yeah, I know.

16:45.600 --> 16:47.280
Bloody rotten agent.

16:47.400 --> 16:48.600
But what can we do?

16:48.720 --> 16:50.320
He's our man, so we
take what we can get.

